data.description: Desirable home! Bathroom is partially updated, Dining Room slider and covered deck. Oversized garage in back of home with alley access & parking for two vehicles. Fenced private backyard. Cute covered front porch. Laundry room off the kitchen. Primary bedroom on main level, two other rooms upstairs. Updated laminate flooring. Bring your own touch to this charming bungalow.
